## Accessibility Requirements

### Text Formatting
```css
/* Content structure */
.content-block {
  max-width: 800px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

/* Headers */
h1, h2, h3 {
  margin-top: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  clear: both;
}

/* Lists */
ul, ol {
  margin-left: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
```

### Content Structure
```html
<!-- Progressive disclosure pattern -->
<article class="content-section">
  <h2>Main Topic</h2>
  <p class="summary">Brief overview</p>
  
  <details>
    <summary>Learn More</summary>
    <div class="detailed-content">
      [Detailed information]
    </div>
  </details>
</article>
```

