## Content Review Process

### Review Checklist
```markdown
1. Accuracy
   - Facts verified
   - Links checked
   - Resources current

2. Clarity
   - Clear purpose
   - Actionable steps
   - Defined terms

3. Accessibility
   - Reading level
   - Clear structure
   - Alt text
   - Transcripts

4. Compliance
   - Disclaimers
   - Privacy
   - Legal requirements

5. Brand Alignment
   - Voice/tone
   - Value proposition
   - Call to action
```

